{"tid":2496649,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"凍食出前一丁（純文字討論）","createTime":"2021-04-20T03:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T13:41:19.000Z","uid":58963,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e30cd9d6e0a9328ebe248c6c5f4eba8974e9e14e","tid":2496649,"uid":58963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:24:30.000Z","msg":"做法如下：<br />\n<br />\n1）煮麵，直到你認為口感OK為止<br />\n2）過冷河（用過濾水過，二到三次就完全凍曬）<br />\n3）落碗，落味粉（似乎口味可以加麻醬、蝦米辣椒醬等）<br />\n4）落凍滾水，撈勻直到咸度味道OK為止<br />\n5）選擇性加配菜（最好係凍）<br />\n<br />\n煮過幾次，之後就無興趣再正常咁熱食出前一丁，除非等到冬天啦。夏天凍食出前一丁，食到好清涼。而且雖然以為凍水冲味粉會令到個麵唔入味，但呢個做法會令到你更加感受到d味（就好似食壽司咁），唔會因為熱力而需要用到好重口味既味粉或者辣椒。推薦加麻醬，酸酸尾尾更加適合夏天。"},{"pid":"459cb32eead80a086bea100da6e55077e9fe5e7f","tid":2496649,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:30:14.000Z","msg":"純文字討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afac7a8861617dabe370ec0a326196769f4e3329","tid":2496649,"uid":2403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:33:00.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"4bc09869faa49e1887b6e27ed7fed449d67855b2","tid":2496649,"uid":58963,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"459cb32eead80a086bea100da6e55077e9fe5e7f","tid":2496649,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:30:14.000Z","msg":"純文字討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:34:04.000Z","msg":"無圖。<br />\n外觀同出前一丁無任何分別。<br />\n只不過係凍既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔記得講仲可以放好耐都唔霖。"},{"pid":"053ac0116261a1294e26d4862f5d08054d042d0a","tid":2496649,"uid":140583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:35:14.000Z","msg":"你冷靜啲啦"},{"pid":"8c1f111e64b0e076db6f16377f80631d48050b63","tid":2496649,"uid":12034,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:47:31.000Z","msg":"弱智 不如生咬"},{"pid":"0f52104186cbf0053cf6d686a7a1376805d13a49","tid":2496649,"uid":58963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c1f111e64b0e076db6f16377f80631d48050b63","tid":2496649,"uid":12034,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:47:31.000Z","msg":"弱智 不如生咬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:52:03.000Z","msg":"咁你生咬開，就唔好試咁樣煮啦。"},{"pid":"64831912fe837d1d2c6c44be422efe6e345ee669","tid":2496649,"uid":24596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T13:41:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}